'''Kamila Bobr''' (born 7 May 1997) is a Belarusian [[Canoe sprint|sprint canoeist]].<ref>[http://results.digicorp.hu/athlete/16799035 Digicorp profile]</ref>

She participated at the [[2018 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships]].<ref>[https://timetable.canoesprintportugal.com/uploads/XML_Provas/39/pdf/198.pdf C-2 200 m results]</ref>

