'''Vladislav Blintsov''' (born 5 April 1996) is a Russian [[Canoe sprint|sprint canoeist]].

He participated at the [[2018 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships]].<ref>[https://timetable.canoesprintportugal.com/uploads/XML_Provas/39/pdf/202.pdf K-2 500 m results]</ref>

